# IMPORTANT: examples/ and cookbook/ are intentionally NOT excluded.
# They are part of the agent-readiness story: AI coding agents read
# `examples/<component>.tsx` and `cookbook/<recipe>.tsx` to learn the
# canonical usage of every primitive. Excluding them would defeat the
# purpose of llms.txt. They are also explicitly listed in package.json
# `files` so they always ship.
